						<Splash class="animate" fill="var(--c-yellow)" width={64} height={64} />
						<h3 class="service c yellow">Brand<br /> Design</h3>
						<p class="desc">Struggling to explain who you are, or why people should care? Let's fix that.</p>
						<Button class="yellow round arrow outline fs-1" text="Starting From: R 4 500" />
					</div>
					<div class="back bg orange grid">
						<h4 class="c-text ct-yellow">What it is:</h4>
						<p>Conversion-focused websites built for speed, clarity, and growth.</p>
						<h4 class="c-text ct-yellow">Why it matters:</h4>
						<p>
							It's your brand's home. It should work 24/7 to bring in leads, explain what you do, and make a killer
							first impression.
						</p>
						<h4 class="c-text ct-yellow">What you get:</h4>
						<p>
							Mobile-optimised, SEO-ready builds 4-10 page options based on your needs Google Analytics, SSL, and speed
							boosts Ongoing support, maintenance, and tweaks.
						</p>
						<Button href="https://connect.inkfish.co.za/hello/" class="yellow round fs-1" text="Book a Discover Call" />
